<import data-ib-structured-id="0"  src="../../../common/head.wxml" />
<import data-ib-structured-id="1"  src="../../../common/foot.wxml" />

<view class="container page" data-weui-theme="{{theme}}" data-ib-structured-id="2">
  <template data-ib-structured-id="3"  is="head" data="{{title: 'camera'}}"/>

  <view class="page-body" data-ib-structured-id="4">
    <view class="page-body-wrapper" data-ib-structured-id="5">
      <camera
        mode="scanCode"
        flash="off"
        bindscancode="scanCode"
        binderror="error"
       data-ib-structured-id="6">
      </camera>
      <view class="btn-area" data-ib-structured-id="7">
        <button type="primary" bindtap="navigateBack" data-ib-structured-id="8">
          返回正常模式
        </button>
      </view>
      <form data-ib-structured-id="9">
        <view class="page-section" data-ib-structured-id="10">
          <view class="weui-cells weui-cells_after-title" data-ib-structured-id="11">
            <view class="weui-cell weui-cell_input" data-ib-structured-id="12">
              <view class="weui-cell__hd" data-ib-structured-id="13">
                <view class="weui-label" data-ib-structured-id="14">类型</view>
              </view>
              <view class="weui-cell__bd" data-ib-structured-id="15">
                {{ result.type }}
              </view>
            </view>
            <view class="weui-cell weui-cell_input" data-ib-structured-id="16">
              <view class="weui-cell__hd" data-ib-structured-id="17">
                <view class="weui-label" data-ib-structured-id="18">结果</view>
              </view>
              <view class="weui-cell__bd" data-ib-structured-id="19">
                {{ result.result }}
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </form>
    </view>
  </view>

  <template data-ib-structured-id="20"  is="foot" />
</view>
